    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "**Setup Services (one-time):**\n- Swiss Association formation with licensed local counsel\n- Registered address in Zug\n- VAT documentation\n- Contract templates\n\n**Recurring Services:**\n- Annual tax filing\n- Monthly accounting & close\n- Monthly expense reports\n- Invoice management\n- Reimbursement management\n- Expense policies (role-based)\n- Contributor onboarding & operations\n- Multi-currency payouts\n- Dedicated ops support\n\n**Advanced tier adds:**\n- Multiple entities\n- Dedicated account manager\n- Admin portal\n- Custom workflows & reporting\n- Add-ons: exchange setup, banking, AML monitoring\n\nThe setup process: initial consultation \u2192 KYB/KYC verification \u2192 founding meeting with licensed Swiss counsel \u2192 entity registration \u2192 ongoing operational services begin immediately.\n\nFacet categories: SNO Function (Operational Hub for Open Source Builders), Legal Entity (Swiss Association, BVI Entity), Anonymity (High/Highest), Team (Remote/Local).",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:38.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:38.000Z"
    }
  },
